nalian.org/2015/01/20/mary-oliver-molly-malone-cook-our-world/">Mary Oliver on What Attention Really Means and Her Moving Elegy for Her Soul Mate</a></h5><div class="clear"></div><a href="https://www.themarginalian.org/2016/03/16/rebecca-solnit-hope-in-the-dark-2/"><img width="300" height="158" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/mrgauguinsheart0.jpg?fit=300%2C158&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="Rebecca Solnit on Hope in Dark Times, Resisting the Defeatism of Easy Despair, and What Victory Really Means for Movements of Social Change" loading="lazy" /></a><h5><a href="https://www.themarginalian.org/2016/03/16/rebecca-solnit-hope-in-the-dark-2/">Rebecca Solnit on Hope in Dark Times, Resisting the Defeatism of Easy Despair, and What Victory Really Means for Movements of Social Change</a></h5><div class="clear"></div><h3 class="more_link"><a href="/favorite-reads/">see more</a></h3></div></aside><aside id="brainpickings_related_reads_widget-3" class="widget widget_brainpickings_related_reads_widget"><div id="related_reads"><h1><span>Related Reads</span></h1><a href="https://www.themarginalian.org/2014/03/07/richard-feynman-rubber-bands/"><img width="300" height="157" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/feynman.jpg?fit=300%2C157&amp;ssl=1" class=" wp-post-image jetpack-lazy-image" alt="The Miraculous in the Mundane: Richard Feynman Explains How Rubber Bands Work" data-lazy-srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/feynman.jpg?w=698&amp;ssl=1 698w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/feynman.jpg?resize=300%2C157&amp;ssl=1 300w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" data-lazy-src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/feynman.jpg?fit=300%2C157&amp;ssl=1&amp;is-pending-load=1"></a><h5><a href="https://www.themarginalian.org/2014/03/07/richard-feynman-rubber-bands/" class="yellow">The Miraculous in the Mundane: Richard Feynman Explains How Rubber Bands Work</a></h5><a href="https://www.themarginalian.org/2014/01/06/the-universe-in-a-glass-of-wine-feynman/"><img width="320" height="168" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/glass-1.jpg?fit=320%2C168&amp;ssl=1" class=" wp-post-image jetpack-lazy-image" alt="The Universe in a Glass of Wine: Richard Feynman on How Everything Connects, Animated" data-lazy-srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/glass-1.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/glass-1.jpg?resize=240%2C126&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/glass-1.jpg?resize=320%2C168&amp;ssl=1 320w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px" data-lazy-src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/glass-1.jpg?fit=320%2C168&amp;ssl=1&amp;is-pending-load=1"></a><h5><a href="https://www.themarginalian.org/2014/01/06/the-universe-in-a-glass-of-wine-feynman/" class="yellow">The Universe in a Glass of Wine: Richard Feynman on How Everything Connects, Animated</a></h5><a href="https://www.themarginalian.org/2012/05/11/richard-feynman-key-to-science/"><img width="198" height="300" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/feynman_pleasure1.jpg?fit=198%2C300&amp;ssl=1" class=" wp-post-image jetpack-lazy-image" alt="Richard Feynman Reveals the Key to Science in 63 Seconds" data-lazy-srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/feynman_pleasure1.jpg?w=300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/feynman_pleasure1.jpg?resize=198%2C300&amp;ssl=1 198w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 198px) 100vw, 198px" data-lazy-src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/feynman_pleasure1.jpg?fit=198%2C300&amp;ssl=1&amp;is-